attributes.additional_details:
INDEPENDENCE: outside EU Common policies on Agriculture, Fisheries, VAT, Foreign, Defence, Trade & European Court of Justice; 
INFLUENCE: Not bound by EU common position on international bodies (eg-WTO) & have an independent voice at a global regulatory level;
CONTINUITY: access to single market, market for financial services & freedom to work & live in EEA states;
SIMPLICITY: The UK is already a signatory to the EEA;
FLEXIBILITY: implement immigration controls (as per Lichtenstein, EFTA member)
